<div class="privacy-content">

<h4>Information We Collect</h4>

<p>
Our appointment booking system collects personal information such as your name,
email address, phone number, and appointment details in order to provide a smooth
healthcare booking experience.
</p>

<br>

<h4>How We Use Your Information</h4>

<p>
The information collected is used to:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Schedule and manage doctor appointments</li>
<li>Send appointment confirmations</li>
<li>Improve our healthcare services</li>
<li>Provide customer support</li>
</ul>

<br>

<h4>Data Security</h4>

<p>
We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information
from unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse.
</p>

<br>

<h4>Third-Party Services</h4>

<p>
We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties except when required
to deliver medical services or comply with legal requirements.
</p>

<br>

<h4>Contact Us</h4>

<p>
If you have any questions regarding our privacy policy, please contact our
support team.
</p>

